{"tha-ap271:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap271:0.2":"Padumukkhipavagga ","tha-ap271:0.3":"9 Upagatasayattheraapadana ","tha-ap271:1.1":"“Himavantassa vemajjhe, ","tha-ap271:1.2":"saro asi sunimmito; ","tha-ap271:1.3":"Tatthaham rakkhaso asim, ","tha-ap271:1.4":"hethasilo bhayanako. ","tha-ap271:2.1":"Anukampako karuniko, ","tha-ap271:2.2":"vipassi lokanayako; ","tha-ap271:2.3":"Mamuddharitukamo so, ","tha-ap271:2.4":"agacchi mama santikam. ","tha-ap271:3.1":"Upagatam mahaviram, ","tha-ap271:3.2":"devadevam narasabham; ","tha-ap271:3.3":"Asaya abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap271:3.4":"avandim satthuno aham. ","tha-ap271:4.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap271:4.2":"yam vandim purisuttamam; ","tha-ap271:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap271:4.4":"vandanaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap271:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap271:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap271:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap271:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma upagatasayo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap271:7.1":"Upagatasayattherassapadanam navamam. "}